Examples <https://github.com/platformio/platformio-examples/>`__ |\n27: `Docs <https://docs.platformio.org?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_ |\n28: `Donate <https://platformio.org/donate?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_ |\n29: `Contact Us <https://piolabs.com/?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n30: \n31: **Social:** `LinkedIn <https://www.linkedin.com/company/platformio/>`_ |\n32: `Twitter <https://twitter.com/PlatformIO_Org>`_ |\n33: `Facebook <https://www.facebook.com/platformio>`_ |\n34: `Community Forums <https://community.platformio.org?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n35: \n36: .. image:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/platformio/platformio-web/develop/app/images/platformio-ide-laptop.png\n37:     :target: https://platformio.org?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core\n38: \n39: `PlatformIO <https://platformio.org>`_: Your Gateway to Embedded Software Development Excellence.\n40: \n41: Unlock the true potential of embedded software development with\n42: PlatformIO's collaborative ecosystem, embracing declarative principles,\n43: test-driven methodologies, and modern toolchains for unrivaled success.\n44: \n45: * Open source, maximum permissive Apache 2.0 license\n46: * Cross-platform IDE and Unified Debugger\n47: * Static Code Analyzer and Remote Unit Testing\n48: * Multi-platform and Multi-architecture Build System\n49: * Firmware File Explorer and Memory Inspection\n50: \n51: Get Started\n52: -----------\n53: \n54: * `What is PlatformIO? <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/what-is-platformio.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n55: * `PlatformIO IDE <https://platformio.org/platformio-ide?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n56: * `PlatformIO Core (CLI) <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/core.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n57: * `Project Examples <https://github.com/platformio/platformio-examples?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`__\n58: \n59: Solutions\n60: ---------\n61: \n62: * `Library Management <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/librarymanager/index.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n63: * `Desktop IDEs Integration <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/ide.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n64: * `Continuous Integration <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/ci/index.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n65: \n66: **Advanced**\n67: \n68: * `Debugging <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/plus/debugging.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n69: * `Unit Testing <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/advanced/unit-testing/index.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n70: * `Static Code Analysis <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/plus/pio-check.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n71: * `Remote Development <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/plus/pio-remote.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n72: \n73: Registry\n74: --------\n75: \n76: * `Libraries <https://registry.platformio.org/search?t=library&utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n77: * `Development Platforms <https://registry.platformio.org/search?t=platform&utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n78: * `Development Tools <https://registry.platformio.org/search?t=tool&utm_source=github&utm_medium=core>`_\n79: \n80: Contributing\n81: ------------\n82: \n83: See `contributing guidelines <https://github.com/platformio/platformio/blob/develop/CONTRIBUTING.md>`_.\n84: \n85: Telemetry / Privacy Policy\n86: --------------------------\n87: \n88: Share minimal diagnostics and usage information to help us make PlatformIO better.\n89: It is enabled by default. For more information see:\n90: \n91: * `Telemetry Setting <https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/userguide/cmd_settings.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core#enable-telemetry>`_\n92: \n93: License\n94: -------\n95: \n96: Copyright (c) 2014-present PlatformIO <contact@platformio.org>\n97: \n98: The PlatformIO is licensed under the permissive Apache 2.0 license,\n99: so you can use it in both commercial and personal projects with confidence.\n100: \n101: .. image:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vshymanskyy/StandWithUkraine/main/banner-direct.svg\n102:     :target: https://github.com/vshymanskyy/StandWithUkraine/blob/main/docs/README.md\n103:     :alt:  SWUbanner\n\n(End of file - total 103 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"PlatformIO Core\n===============\n\n.. image:: https://github.com/platformio/platformio-core/workflows/Core/badge.svg\n    :target: https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/core/index.html\n    :alt:  CI Build for PlatformIO Core\n.. image:: https://github.com/platformio/platformio-core/workflows/Docs/badge.svg\n    :target: https://docs.platformio.org?utm_source=github&utm_medium=core\n    :alt:  CI Build for Docs\n.. image:: https://github.com/platformio/platformio-core/workflows/Examples/badge.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/platformio/platformio-examples\n    :alt:  CI Build for dev-platform examples\n.. image:: https://github.com/platformio/platformio-core/workflows/Projects/badge.svg\n    :target: https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/tutorials/index.html#projects\n    :alt:  CI Build for the Community Projects\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/platformio.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/platformio/\n    :alt: Latest Version\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/PlatformIO-Labs-orange.svg\n   :alt: PlatformIO Labs","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"README.rst","time":{"start":1776094944316,"end":1776094944329}}}]}
